# FeedForward

A modern feedback explorer built with **React**, **TypeScript**, and **Vite**.

## Features

- Add, view, upvote(needs improvement), and delete feedback items
- Group feedback by category (Bug, Feature, Improvement)
- Search and sort feedback
- Toast notifications for actions
- Accessible, responsive UI
- Optional: JWT authentication for restricted actions

## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- Node.js (v18+ recommended)
- npm or yarn

### Installation

```bash
npm install
```

### Running the App

```bash
npm run dev
```

The app will start on [http://localhost:5173](http://localhost:5173) by default.

### Building for Production

```bash
npm run build
```

### Linting

```bash
npm run lint
```

